txt.en: When you or your Shield-brother is attacked, both have a chance to be healed.\n\nHits against you or your Shield-brother reduce the cooldown of At the Fore and Strength in Numbers.
When you or your Shield-brother is attacked, both have a chance to be healed.
Hits against you or your Shield-brother reduce the cooldown of Strength in Numbers by 1s and At the Fore by 2s \n\n These effects can only occur once every 5 seconds per brother.
